        <div class="about-us-text">
            <h2 class="text-start">Who We Are</h2>
            <p class="text-start">Cabbage Coins is a Buyer and Seller of Rare Coins, Gold, and Silver Bars located right in the heart of beautiful Lancaster County Pennsylvania. A few facts about Cabbage Coins:<!--{{ metadata.aboutustext }}--></p>
            <ul>
                <li>We want to be your coin dealer. We buy rare coin collections and offer free appraisals. Give us a call to discuss the collection and we'll help answer questions and give an idea around value. </li>
                <li>Our bread and butter are nice, encapsulated, better date coins for the astute collector. Visit our "Inventory" page to see the current collection for purchase.</li>
                <li>Lancaster County, PA is our home, but we're happy to travel across the mid-Atlantic to check out coin collections and scope out local coin shows for new buying opportunities</li>
                <li>We visit most of the major national and local coin shows - if you ever see us set up as a dealer - please come by, check out our coins and say 'hello!'</li>
                <li>Be sure to check out the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@cabbage_coins" target="_blank" style="color:#6289c1;">YouTube podcast</a> where the mission is educating viewers, inspiring new collectors and elevating the quality of collections</li>
            </ul>
