                        <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:16px; color:#333; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:10px;">Owned and operated since 2021 by <strong>Tony Gryckiewicz</strong> — Professional Numismatist and ANA Life Member #7339.</p>
                        <p style="font-family:'Roboto'; font-size:16px; color:#333; line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:16px;">Tony's background is in data analytics and operational strategy for the mortgage servicing industry. After starting Cabbage Coins as a side-hustle in 2021, it has grown to a full-time gig. In Summer 2025, Tony finished his final consulting contract and went all-in with Cabbage Coins!</p>
